  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 - \u0dbd\u0dda\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pohottu inquires from the Chairman-Secretary",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. G. L. Peiris, the chairman of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, has asked the Secretary General Sagara Kariyawasam in a letter on what basis the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna announced that it would support Ranil Wickramasinghe in the election of a suitable candidate for the currently vacant presidential post.",
        "The Secretary of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Mr. Sagara Kariyawasam stated in a statement yesterday that Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has decided to provide support to Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe in the election of a new president.",
        "The Chairman of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has forwarded this letter requesting an answer to that announcement. The article states:"
      ],
